message.body: Hello! I am good. How about yourself?
I'm doing very well, thank you! How are things where you are?
That's good to hear! Things are busy. Haha. Helping out with the family business today. How about over there?
Doing pretty good just relaxing today. Going on vacation tomorrow :)
Oh how nice! Where are you vacationing to?
Soak city lol it's a water park in California
That's so exciting! Hehe. I love California. The weather is so nice.
It's alright it's been pretty hot lately
Yeah but at least it's not crazy cold in the winter
Yeah, though where I live I wish it would snow sometimes!
Yeah snow is nice once in a while. But it's a bit difficult to deal with when driving lol
